	<h2>Design System</h2>
	<div class="dsystem-topcols">
		<div>Building a scalable design system to improve consistency, efficiency, and collaboration across digital products. <br><br> As the product ecosystem expanded, maintaining consistency across interfaces became increasingly challenging. Different teams were creating similar UI elements independently, leading to duplicated components, inconsistent patterns, and increased design debt. <br><br> The goal was to create a centralized design system that would establish a shared visual language, improve collaboration between design and development teams, and accelerate future product development.</div>
		<div class="dsystem-topcols__right">
			<div>
				<h3>The Chellenge</h3>
				<p>Product growth led to inconsistent patterns, duplicated components, and inefficient design workflows.</p>
			</div>
			<div>
				<h3>Goal</h3>
				<p>Create a scalable system that enables faster and more consistent product development.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
